								<button class="btn btn-default pull-right" type="submit">Skicka</button>
							</div>
						</form>

						<div id="feedback-thread" class="col-xs-12">
							<ul class="media-list">
								<li class="media">
							        <a class="pull-left" href="#">
							          <img class="media-object img-circle" src="img/librarian.jpg">
							        </a>
							        <div class="media-body">
							          <p><span class="badge">2013-12-01 13:22</span> Cras sit amet nibh libero, in gravida nulla. Nulla vel metus scelerisque ante sollicitudin commodo. Cras purus odio, vestibulum in vulputate at, tempus viverra turpis.</p>
